Name: Apple MacBook Pro 2020

Processor: 1.4GHz quad‑core Intel Core i5, Turbo Boost up to 3.9GHz, with 128MB of eDRAM
Ports: Two Thunderbolt 3 (USB‑C) ports with support for: Charging, DisplayPort, Thunderbolt(up to 40 Gb / s), USB 3.1 Gen 2(up to 10 Gb / s)

Communication: Wi‑Fi 802.11 ac Wi‑ Fi wireless networking, IEEE 802.11 a / b / g / n compatible, Bluetooth 5.0 wireless technology
